msgctxt "1596_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Hi! Nice to meet you!"
msgstr "¡Hola! ¡Encantada de conocerte!"

msgctxt "1608_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm Kazuma Kiryu. Nice to meet you."
msgstr "Soy Kazuma Kiryu. Encantado de conocerte."

msgctxt "1620_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "You look pretty laid-back."
msgstr "You look pretty laid-back."

msgctxt "1632_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "You'll have to be a little more energetic if you want to drink with me!"
msgstr "¡Tendrás que tener un poco más de energía si quieres beber conmigo!"

msgctxt "1644_Kiryu"
msgid "Hey, you're not drunk already, are you?"
msgstr "Oye, aún no estás borracho, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "1656_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Not yet! What kind of alcohol do you like? I'll drink whatever you order!"
msgstr "Todavía no. ¿Qué tipo de alcohol te gusta? ¡Beberé lo sea que pidas!"

msgctxt "1668_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm a beer man, myself."
msgstr "I'm a beer man, myself."

msgctxt "1680_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Beer, huh? There's nothing like a cold one after a hard day's work! Of course, in my case, drinking is my work."
msgstr "Cerveza, ¿eh? No hay nada como una cerveza fría después de un duro día de trabajo. Claro que, en mi caso, beber es mi trabajo."

msgctxt "1692_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Are you on your way home from work?"
msgstr "Are you on your way home from work?"

msgctxt "1704_Kiryu"
msgid "In a way."
msgstr "En cierto modo."

msgctxt "1716_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "You work in an outfit like that? I'm guessing you're not an average businessman."
msgstr "¿Usted trabaja vestido de esa manera? Supongo que no es un hombre de negocios promedio."

msgctxt "1728_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, that depends on your point of view."
msgstr "Bueno, eso depende de tu punto de vista."

msgctxt "1740_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Oh come on! What do you do? I have to know!"
msgstr "¡Vamos! ¿A qué se dedica? ¡Tengo que saberlo!"

msgctxt "1752_Kiryu"
msgid "Whiskey. No question."
msgstr "Whiskey. Sin duda."

msgctxt "1764_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Whiskey, huh? Hmm. That would be fine, I guess..."
msgstr "Whisky, ¿eh? Hmm. Eso estaría bien, supongo..."

msgctxt "1776_Kiryu"
msgid "Is there a problem?"
msgstr "¿Hay algún problema?"

msgctxt "1788_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Well, I like whiskey. But when I drink it, I turn into a pretty annoying person."
msgstr "Bueno, me gusta el whisky. Pero cuando lo bebo, me vuelvo una persona bastante molesta."

msgctxt "1800_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I butt into conversations and only talk about myself. The club asked me not to drink whiskey if I can help it."
msgstr "Me entrometo en las conversaciones y sólo hablo de mí misma. El club me pidió que no bebiera whisky si podia evitarlo."

msgctxt "1812_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "But I'll be happy to drink it if you want me to!"
msgstr "¡Pero estaré encantada de beberlo si quieres!"

msgctxt "1824_Kiryu"
msgid "No, that's okay."
msgstr "No, no pasa nada."

msgctxt "1836_Kiryu"
msgid "You might be surprised, but I like champagne."
msgstr "Puede que te sorprendas, pero a mí me gusta el champán."

msgctxt "1848_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Really? That is kind of a surprise. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Really? That is kind of a surprise. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "1860_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Does that mean you're rich?"
msgstr "¿Eso significa que usted es rico?"

msgctxt "1872_Kiryu"
msgid "Do I look rich to you?"
msgstr "¿Te parezco rico?"

msgctxt "1884_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Hmm... Well, you look like you might have money, but then again maybe not."
msgstr "Hmm... Well, you look like you might have money, but then again maybe not."

msgctxt "1896_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "But champagne sounds great! Excuse me! One bottle of <Color:7>Gold Champagne<Color:Default> for Kiryu-san!"
msgstr "¡Pero champán suena genial! ¡Disculpe! ¡Una botella de <Color:7>Champán Dorado<Color:Default> para Kiryu-san!"

msgctxt "1908_Kiryu"
msgid "Hey, I didn't order that."
msgstr "Oye, yo no ordene eso."

msgctxt "1920_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "You think I've grown up?"
msgstr "You think I've grown up?"

msgctxt "1932_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "What do you think my special talent is?"
msgstr "What do you think my special talent is?"

msgctxt "1944_Kiryu"
msgid "I don't know. What?"
msgstr "I don't know. What?"

msgctxt "1956_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Drinking! I can drink anybody under the table!"
msgstr "Drinking! I can drink anybody under the table!"

msgctxt "1968_Kiryu"
msgid "You seem pretty confident."
msgstr "You seem pretty confident."

msgctxt "1980_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Of course I am! Want to try drinking with me one-on-one next time?"
msgstr "Of course I am! Want to try drinking with me one-on-one next time?"

msgctxt "1992_Kiryu"
msgid "You mean you want me to request you?"
msgstr "¿Me estás pidiendo que te solicite?"

msgctxt "2004_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "You think I've grown up?"
msgstr "You think I've grown up?"

msgctxt "2016_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I just want a chance to talk more with you."
msgstr "I just want a chance to talk more with you."

msgctxt "2028_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. That so?"
msgstr "Je, je, ¿en serio?"

msgctxt "2040_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I like men with muscular arms like you. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "I like men with muscular arms like you. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2052_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "So I hope you'll come and see me again."
msgstr "So I hope you'll come and see me again."

msgctxt "2064_Kiryu"
msgid "I wouldn't mind that, but you'll have to have your drinking contests with somebody else."
msgstr "I wouldn't mind that, but you'll have to have your drinking contests with somebody else."

msgctxt "2076_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Haha! All right, then. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Haha! All right, then. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2088_Kiryu"
msgid "I prefer to take my time when I drink. It's a waste to just chug it down."
msgstr "I prefer to take my time when I drink. It's a waste to just chug it down."

msgctxt "2100_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Oh, sure. You're just scared that I'll beat you."
msgstr "Oh, sure. You're just scared that I'll beat you."

msgctxt "2112_Kiryu"
msgid "Hardly."
msgstr "Para nada."

msgctxt "2124_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Hmph. You're not much fun."
msgstr "Hmph. You're not much fun."

msgctxt "2136_Kiryu"
msgid "No?"
msgstr "¿No?"

msgctxt "2148_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "This isn't your first time at a hostess club, is it? Are you nervous?"
msgstr "This isn't your first time at a hostess club, is it? Are you nervous?"

msgctxt "2160_Kiryu"
msgid "Not at all. Actually, I'm pretty relaxed. I just want to sit back and enjoy my time here."
msgstr "Not at all. Actually, I'm pretty relaxed. I just want to sit back and enjoy my time here."

msgctxt "2172_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "All right. I'll do my best to help you relax if you come and see me again."
msgstr "All right. I'll do my best to help you relax if you come and see me again."

msgctxt "2184_Kiryu"
msgid "You sure you don't need a handicap?"
msgstr "You sure you don't need a handicap?"

msgctxt "2196_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Oh, come on. You don't think I need special treatment because I'm a woman, do you?"
msgstr "Oh, come on. You don't think I need special treatment because I'm a woman, do you?"

msgctxt "2208_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "You're the one who'll need a handicap!"
msgstr "You're the one who'll need a handicap!"

msgctxt "2220_Kiryu"
msgid "Okay. What do I get if you lose?"
msgstr "Okay. What do I get if you lose?"

msgctxt "2232_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Well... I could become your girlfriend. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Well... I could become your girlfriend. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2244_Kiryu"
msgid "All right, then, let's get started."
msgstr "All right, then, let's get started."

msgctxt "2256_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Hey! I was kidding! Stop looking at me like that!"
msgstr "Hey! I was kidding! Stop looking at me like that!"

msgctxt "2268_Kiryu"
msgid "Hehehe."
msgstr "Je, je, je."

msgctxt "2280_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Are you enjoying your drink?"
msgstr "Kiryu-san! Are you enjoying your drink?"

msgctxt "2292_Kiryu"
msgid "Sure. This club has a good selection."
msgstr "Sure. This club has a good selection."

msgctxt "2304_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I know! I'm glad I decided to work here. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Lo sé! Me alegro de haber decidido trabajar aquí. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2316_Kiryu"
msgid "Aren't most girls here for the money? You won't have time to snag any customers if you just drink."
msgstr "¿La mayoría de las chicas no están aquí por el dinero? No tendrás tiempo de enganchar a ningún cliente si sólo bebes."

msgctxt "2328_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I'm happy as long as I make enough to get by. And as long as I can drink the good stuff! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "I'm happy as long as I make enough to get by. And as long as I can drink the good stuff! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2340_Kiryu"
msgid "Hehe. I see."
msgstr "Jeje. Ya veo."

msgctxt "2352_Himeka"
msgid "The dialogue will end after one round if you've entered a club more than once. Please report when this message is displayed."
msgstr "La conversación terminará después de una ronda cuando entre al club más de una vez. Por favor reporte si este mensaje es mostrado."

msgctxt "2364_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Hey, Kiryu-san. Why didn't you request me today?"
msgstr "Hola, Kiryu-san. ¿Por qué no me solicito hoy?"

msgctxt "2376_Kiryu"
msgid "I thought this would be a nice change. You'd drink the same thing every day, right?"
msgstr "I thought this would be a nice change. You'd drink the same thing every day, right?"

msgctxt "2388_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "So you're tired of me?"
msgstr "So you're tired of me?"

msgctxt "2400_Kiryu"
msgid "No, no. This was just a one time thing. I'll definitely request you next time."
msgstr "No, no. Esto fue sólo una vez. Definitivamente te solicitare la próxima vez."

msgctxt "2412_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Really!? Okay then. That's a promise. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Really!? Okay then. That's a promise. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2424_Himeka"
msgid "The dialogue will end after one round if you've entered a club more than once. Please notify a programmer if this message is displayed."
msgstr "The dialogue will end after one round if you've entered a club more than once. Please notify a programmer if this message is displayed."

msgctxt "2580_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Hi! Nice to meet you!"
msgstr "¡Hola! ¡Encantada de conocerle!"

msgctxt "2592_Tanimura"
msgid "Hi. I'm Tanimura."
msgstr "Hola. Me llamo Tanimura."

msgctxt "2604_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "There's nothing like a nice drink after work!"
msgstr "¡No hay nada como una buena bebida después del trabajo!"

msgctxt "2616_Tanimura"
msgid "Aren't you at work right now?"
msgstr "¿Pero no estás trabajando ahora?"

msgctxt "2628_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I was thinking about you, silly."
msgstr "Lo decía por usted, bobito."

msgctxt "2640_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Come on then. Drink up!"
msgstr "Vamos. ¡Beba!"

msgctxt "2652_Tanimura"
msgid "You don't waste any time, do you?"
msgstr "No pierdes el tiempo, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "2664_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Do you like any sports?"
msgstr "¿Le gusta algún deporte?"

msgctxt "2676_Tanimura"
msgid "Not really... But you could say I like martial arts."
msgstr "No, la verdad que no... Pero se podría decir que me gustan las artes marciales."

msgctxt "2688_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Oh? Do you do any martial arts?"
msgstr "¿Ah, sí? ¿Práctica algún tipo de arte marcial?"

msgctxt "2700_Tanimura"
msgid "Jujitsu, mostly. I also had to do judo and kendo as part of my training."
msgstr "Sí, sobre todo, jujutsu. También tuve que hacer un poco de judo y kendo como parte de mi entrenamiento."

msgctxt "2712_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Training? Interesting! Tell me more! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Oh, ¿entrenamiento? Qué interesante, ¡cuénteme más! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2724_Tanimura"
msgid "But I came here to get away from work..."
msgstr "Pero vine aquí para alejarme del trabajo..."

msgctxt "2736_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Welcome! You must be tired! I'm sure you've been working hard! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Bienvenido! ¡Debes estar cansado! ¡Seguro que has trabajado mucho! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2748_Tanimura"
msgid "You're full of energy, as usual."
msgstr "Estás llena de energía, como siempre."

msgctxt "2760_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "What kind of alcohol do you like?"
msgstr "¿Qué tipo de bebida alcohólica le gusta?"

msgctxt "2772_Tanimura"
msgid "I'm not picky. Sometimes I'll drink beer, sometimes I'll drink lao chu."
msgstr "No soy quisquilloso. A veces bebo cerveza y a veces bebo lao chu."

msgctxt "2784_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Lao chu!? You must have a high tolerance, then. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¿¡Lao chu!? Debes tener una alta tolerancia, entonces. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2796_Tanimura"
msgid "Heh. Not really."
msgstr "Je. No realmente."

msgctxt "2808_Himeka"
